{"updated_at": "2011-07-27T17:31:36Z", "repo": "rails", "created_at": "2011-07-27T17:31:36Z", "owner": "rails", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/1665809", "id": 1665809, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/2180", "issue_id": 2180, "user": {"repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gkfabs/repos", "type": "User", "html_url": "https://github.com/gkfabs", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gkfabs/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gkfabs/subscriptions", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gkfabs/following{/other_user}", "gravatar_id": "c8d2d7e1e07aa57dcee128e2ec203e7a", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gkfabs/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/gkfabs", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gkfabs/gists{/gist_id}", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/c8d2d7e1e07aa57dcee128e2ec203e7a?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fc469c3c2df81051245577433d199ef08.png", "id": 58359, "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gkfabs/events{/privacy}", "login": "gkfabs", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gkfabs/received_events", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/gkfabs/followers"}, "body": "The @dirty warning comes from the test test_flush_output_buffer_concats_output_buffer_to_response in the file actionpack/test/template/capture_helper_test.rb\r\n\r\nIn the first call to view.flush_output_buffer, the output_buffer is reseted:\r\nself.output_buffer = output_buffer[0,0]\r\nIf you replace it with self.output_buffer = ActionView::OutputBuffer.new the warning disappear.\r\n\r\nI redo the commit, to take in account this change.\r\nHave a look at b97162f43def97a608405cf7091d96a096711b0d\r\n\r\nThanks\r\nThanks", "_id": {"$oid": "5238476bbd3543c15101108a"}, "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/2180#issuecomment-1665809"}
